{
  "number": 2263,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/2263",
  "title": "feat(publish-script): re-write as js script, allow beta releases",
  "body": "Related to #2056 \r\n\r\nI have re-written the release script in javascript to enhance the user experience when doing a new release and also to allow releases from another branch than develop for beta releases.\r\n\r\nHere is the flow:\r\n\r\n* if branch === develop -> do normal release\r\n* if branch === master -> ask to be on develop for normal release or another branch for beta\r\n* if branch !== develop || branch !== master -> ask if user wants to release a beta\r\n\r\n**In case of beta, ask for a new version number with -beta.x suffix**\r\n\r\n* [x] Allow stable releases\r\n* [x] Allow beta releases\r\n* [x] Revert changes if process does not go until the end\r\n* [x] Refactoring of duplicated code (for different releases cycles)\r\n\r\nResult:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/893837/28581902-e92395c2-7163-11e7-9c14-f4a9b827ae43.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/893837/28581931-fcf30a10-7163-11e7-9400-8a2042257171.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/893837/28581939-0649336e-7164-11e7-93ad-746a3719c301.png)\r\n\r\n",
